
## Development

start the frontend app server:

`npm run startapp`

start the api server:

`npm run startapi`

start the webpack dev server:

`npm run dev:wds`





















### notes for later


ELASTICSEARCH MONGO WITH TRANSPORTER

java8

elasticsearch

https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-sync-transformed-data-from-mongodb-to-elasticsearch-with-transporter-on-ubuntu-16-04


https://www.compose.com/articles/getting-started-with-elasticsearch-and-node/


curl -X PUT "localhost:9200/test3" -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d'
{
  "mappings": {
    "units": {
      "dynamic_templates": [
        {
          "strings": {
            "match_mapping_type": "string",
            "mapping": {
              "type": "text",
              "copy_to": "catch_all"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}'


curl -X DELETE "localhost:9200/test3"



curl -X GET "localhost:9200/test3/_search?pretty=true" -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d'
{
    "query": {
        "match" : {
            "catch_all" : "syria"
        }
    }
}
'

sudo -u elasticsearch h elasticsearch -f
(master)→ sudo su elasticsearch
(master)→ sudo -u elasticsearch elasticsearch
